post.description:
**Privilege**: ConfigureComponents, Login
> **NOTE**: Adding a value of 28 or above will automatically schedule the job for last day of the month.</nl>
> **NOTE**: <!--337236 --> While scheduling a job, if RecurrenceInterval's value is added with a decimal in it, then the job will still be created with the value truncated to the whole number preceding the decimal.
To schedule instantly:</br>
```json
{
    "Payload": {
        "TargetUri": "/redfish/v1/Systems/System.Embedded.1/Bios/Actions/Oem/DellBios.RunBIOSLiveScanning"
    }
}
```
* To enable daily scan scheduling:</br>
```json
{
    "Payload": {
        "TargetUri": "/redfish/v1/Systems/System.Embedded.1/Bios/Actions/Oem/DellBios.RunBIOSLiveScanning"
    },
    "Schedule": {
        "RecurrenceInterval": "P1D"
    }
}
```
* To schedule scanning Monthly:</br>
```json
{
    "Payload": {
        "TargetUri": "/redfish/v1/Systems/System.Embedded.1/Bios/Actions/Oem/DellBios.RunBIOSLiveScanning"
    },
    "Schedule": {
        "EnabledDaysOfMonth": [
            24
        ]
    }
}
```
* To schedule scanning Yearly:</br>
```json
{
    "Payload": {
        "TargetUri": "/redfish/v1/Systems/System.Embedded.1/Bios/Actions/Oem/DellBios.RunBIOSLiveScanning"
    },
    "Schedule": {
        "RecurrenceInterval": "P365D"
    }
}
```
